      private void setValueAt​(Object value, int row, int column, boolean isFire)
      This method check the type of the cell based on the input and cast it into it: Class Name Data Types Description Cell Maria Anders Cell CellNumber Number CellNumber CellString String CellString CellFormula Object CellFormula And after that if it's a formula cell, it calculates the value of the operation, sets it and update SheetStructure.cellFormula otherwise set the value in the JTable and updates all value inside JTable if isFire is true.
